@_zyozyo from K-pop group @twicetagram just linked up with @shenseea on the new track “Distant Lover” alongside a cinematic music video. The genre-blending single brings together K-pop, rap and dance influences for an infectious, summer-ready release.
Exploring the complicated reality of modern dating, the track turns those confusing moments into a powerful anthem. We heard from JIHYO on working with Shenseea and filming the video.
